atar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/61/36176.jpg","floor":"#16-2","id":"1275587","time":"2017-9-8 00:18","userId":"36176","userName":"豆沙包罐头","userSign":"","message":"出资的是委员会，通过各种衍生物赚大钱的也是委员会，被找来负责制作的公司/业者们还是拿自己的苦力钱。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/22/242254.jpg","floor":"#16-3","id":"1275619","time":"2017-9-8 15:04","userId":"242254","userName":"摩卡香又甜","userSign":"","message":"一个季度看10-20部的我还以为自己看的算少的了<br>好吧确实最近几年追的越来越少，因为能让我坚持看完的番越来越少了"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/67/216796.jpg","floor":"#17","id":"1275575","time":"2017-9-7 23:09","userId":"pianer","userName":"骈儿","userSign":"(动画爱好者，不是阿宅)","message":"好好挣钱，养家糊口","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/48/54847.jpg","floor":"#18","id":"1275588","time":"2017-9-8 01:43","userId":"sha1360","userName":"Pnyuu🌟","userSign":"(世界の殼を破られば、我らは生まれずに死んでいく ... ...)","message":"能看的变少了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/32/25/322528.jpg","floor":"#19","id":"1275590","time":"2017-9-8 06:41","userId":"rikkas","userName":"セツミ","userSign":"(どんまい、私〜☆)","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/16.gif\" smileid=\"55\" alt=\"(bgm39)\">老老实实玩黄油","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/11/251156.jpg","floor":"#20","id":"1275599","time":"2017-9-8 11:05","userId":"alchemy313","userName":"果小饼","userSign":"(就当我神经病不好吗)","message":"“能让观众不带脑子看得很开心”的方向","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/35/273577.jpg","floor":"#21","id":"1275616","time":"2017-9-8 14:06","userId":"273577","userName":"SeniY","userSign":"(在水中思考)","message":"吃瓜群众只是有什么看什么<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/94/279427.jpg","floor":"#22","id":"1275862","time":"2017-9-10 05:28","userId":"zakufa782","userName":"zakufa782","userSign":"","message":"反正萝卜片是越来越少了","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/06/130683.jpg","floor":"#23","id":"1275870","ti